name: Priti Yadav
bio: Priti Yadav is an educator, developer and AI/ML enthusiast with expertise in machine learning applications and a strong interest in image processing and analysis. Leading AI-focused initiative, she emphasize collaborative learning and open-source practices. Passionate about interdisciplinary AI applications, my work explores accessibility, productivity, and sustainability. She actively contribute to community-driven AI/ML events. She leads Google Developer Groups Surrey.
